snippet.title: v6.1 Moonshade Epic Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v6.1: Moonshade Epic coming soon!
New S-rank battlesuit Jade Knight for Li Sushang debuts!
Story Chapter XXXII, featured event Midnight Chronicle and awesome bonuses to be released! Stay tuned!
Voice Artists:
Kiana: Rie Kugimiya
Raiden Mei: Miyuki Sawashiro
Prometheus: Kana Asumi
Li Sushang: Misato Fukuen
Gray Serpent: Takatsugu Awazu
Kevin: Satoshi Hino
